Tyrael: Cygnar, take the first corridor on the right and follow it. 
You'll get to the bridge. Cheetah, Tigerhawk, get ready to blast those 
scrap pieces called Predacons to the pits.

The ship went through a last cloud and was now in full view of the 
battle field. It was a dreadful sight from the ground. The ship was 
armed with six laser cannons and two missile bays.

Tyrael: Hydras, I strongly suggest you surrender your forces. I am 
here to claim you and bring you to the Tripredacus Council. I will do 
so even if all that remains of you is a smoldering pile of junk.
